nodes.bodyText:
I wanted to keep it separate, since the requirement is somewhat differet. This secrets_system value is a one time secretused for db encryption and requires a 32 character string.
documentation of hydra uses this command to generate the value:
export SECRETS_SYSTEM=$(export LC_CTYPE=C; cat /dev/urandom | tr -dc 'a-zA-Z0-9' | fold -w 32 | head -n 1)

